from datetime import date, timedelta

# Function to find the last Monday of a given month and year
def last_monday(year, month):
    # Start from the last day of the month
    last_day = date(year, month + 1, 1) - timedelta(days=1)
    # Go back to the last Monday
    while last_day.weekday() != 0:  # 0 is Monday
        last_day -= timedelta(days=1)
    return last_day.day

# Get the last Monday of October 2022
last_monday_october_2022 = last_monday(2022, 10)
